{"tid":1005072,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"Nikon Z7可以話集大成，十年磨一劍之作","createTime":"2019-02-02T03:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T04:21:13.000Z","uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e76e0431988d629f643759dfd102ae1c16f7581","tid":1005072,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WyybGzQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWyybGzQ.png&h=66b899a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對比D850果種吹大左，新機不如D810<br />\nZ7響眾人負期望下，我比佢既表現係壓倒性打低D850<br />\n畫質，同D850一樣，但有五軸防震，D850太易受震模糊既缺點解缺左<br />\n<br />\n發色，用綠色平衡左D850既黃，影人偏白。<br />\n<br />\n對焦快過D850，準過D850，重有眼控。D850唯一贏Z7就係個3D Track<br />\n<br />\n外型就一定Z7<br />\n<br />\n另外，有熱巴代言"},{"pid":"5ecc487656c7b68fe66678a286a73d419199bdae","tid":1005072,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:44:02.000Z","msg":"用 live view揀對焦點每次都要等佢完成一次對焦先可以再揀下一個對焦點。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪弱智架，對於經常要換對焦點既人黎講呢部根本係殘廢機黎。"},{"pid":"6108b743384b304a15b39ccba6bbd1068d124158","tid":1005072,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:45:45.000Z","msg":"仲以為Nikon 終於生性搞返好拍片同live view  點知都仲係咁唔完善"},{"pid":"acab44283b73a28a896e265f6401725d5daab11f","tid":1005072,"uid":15235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:46:26.000Z","msg":"電子垃圾"},{"pid":"148e246ef1e980b7a437f1b9f8186a0b668a9f2a","tid":1005072,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:48:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>樓主唔係狙擊NIKON咩?</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a7f7c9b931ae8cf1ab922a23d7d70ed65ead3c00","tid":1005072,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"148e246ef1e980b7a437f1b9f8186a0b668a9f2a","tid":1005072,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T03:48:11.